' @id(SEQ-WHOLE-MAP-ACCUMULATE)
' @ref(USE-WHOLE-MAP)
'
' Current-side flow as implemented by the "Whole-map baseline" section
' of templates::MDD_CYCLE_SKILL (.claude/.codex/skills/mdd-cycle/SKILL.md)
' plus the bootstrapped .mdd/map/ tree. Agent-driven prose, like the
' rest of /mdd-cycle; mdd-core supplies only the read-side CycleDiff.
'
' @desc(SEQ-WHOLE-MAP-ACCUMULATE, "As-built: /mdd-cycle's Close step folds a closed cycle's @id add/remove sets into the persisted per-concept .mdd/map/ tree (added copied from after/ with ' @cycle provenance, removed dropped, unchanged kept), rewrites manifest.yml, snapshots to .mdd/cycles/<N>/whole/, and /mdd-render rasterizes .mdd/map/**.")
title Accumulate the whole-map baseline at cycle close (current)

participant "/mdd-cycle\n(Close step, SKILL.md)" as Close <<added>>
database ".mdd/cycles/<N>/\nbefore/, after/, whole/" as Snap
collections "CycleDiff per\ntouched concept" as Diff
database ".mdd/map/\n<kind>/<name>.puml\n+ manifest.yml" as Map
participant "/mdd-render" as Render

Close -> Snap : after the cycle's <diagram>.diff.puml\nare written, read before/ and after/
Close -> Diff : @id add/remove/unchanged per concept

loop for each concept <kind>/<name> in after/
  alt .mdd/map/<kind>/<name>.puml absent
    Close -> Map : copy after/ verbatim;\nprepend ' @cycle(<ID>,<N>) per @id
  else exists
    Close -> Map : insert added @ids from after/\ntagged ' @cycle(<ID>,<N>)
    Close -> Map : delete removed @ids + elements\n(net cancel — no ghost)
    note right of Map
      unchanged @ids keep earlier
      ' @cycle(...) provenance.
    end note
  end
end

alt concept in before/ not after/ (file deleted)
  Close -> Map : remove .mdd/map/<kind>/<name>.puml
end

Close -> Map : rewrite manifest.yml\n(version, last_cycle=N, generated_at, files)
Close -> Snap : copy .mdd/map/ -> .mdd/cycles/<N>/whole/
Close -> Render : /mdd-render
Render -> Map : rasterize .mdd/map/**.puml\n-> .mdd/rendered/map/**.svg

note over Map
  Inspection artifact only. /mdd-validate,
  /mdd-review and the /mdd-cycle parity loop
  never read .mdd/map/ (OCL-MAP-* constrain
  WholeMap but are not parity gates).
end note
@enduml
